X-WR-CALNAME:Central disruption
BEGIN:VEVENT
DESCRIPTION:<a href="https://tfl.gov.uk/tube-dlr-overground/status/?Input=&lineIds=&dateTypeSelect=Future%20date&direction=&startDate=2026-06-03T23:00:00&endDate=2026-06-04T22:59:00">Disruption map.</a>\n\nTUBE STRIKE: Some London Underground Tube drivers are planning to take two full days of strike action on Tuesday 2 and Thursday 4 June. Last trains late on Monday and Wednesday nights are expected to operate as normal. Service is expected across most Tube lines on both days. However\, there will be disruption to journeys and service levels will vary across the London Underground network. No service is expected before 0630 and customers are advised to complete journeys by 2100 on both strike days. Some disruption is expected during the early mornings of Wednesday 3 and Friday 5 June as we return our services to normal.
DTEND:20260604T225900Z
DTSTART:20260603T230000Z
SUMMARY:Central: Special Service
UID:48a01fe9-80c5-4f2a-9229-38c93b74ce51@48a0.org
END:VEVENT
